high_descs: Turn right and go to the table
Grab the large knife off of the table
Move slightly to the right
Slice the apple on the table
Move slightly to the left and look down at the table
Put the knife on the table
Move slightly to the right
Grab a slice of the apple
Turn around and go to the fridge
Cool the apple slice in the fridge and then take it out
Turn around and go to the table
Put the apple slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a cold apple slice on the table

high_descs: Turn right, go to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Move a bit to the right
Cut the apple on the table
Move a bit to the left
Put the knife on the table
Move a bit to the right
Pick up an apple piece from the table
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the apple piece in the fridge, wait, pick up the apple piece from the fridge
Turn around, go to the table
Put the apple piece on the table
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, cool a piece of apple

high_descs: Turn left to walk towards the wooden table.
Pick up the leftmost knife from the table.
Turn to face the apple.
Slice the apple with the knife.
Turn to face the table.
Put the knife down on the table.
Turn to face the sliced apple.
Pick up an apple slice from the table.
Turn around to walk to the fridge.
Chill the apple slice in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn around to walk back to the wooden table.
Set the apple slice down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple slice to set on the table.
